accessibility.text: P6: they don't explore [the adoption storyline] obviously because it's a f*****g cartoon […] the graphic novel does do that. actually, this is one of the reasons why i love that one so much.
P9: if [he] were real…if i could get some of [his] wisdom…

P14: the more that you are around them and again it's like the spending time with them - the more you watch the film, then more you know them. […] it sounds ridiculous but because i've known them for such a long time, and they've known me for such a long time, it's almost like a comforting seeing them there and having them with me.
